  <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h1>About SmartPetGuide</h1>

    <p>SmartPetGuide helps pet parents find the best smart devices for their furry family members. From automatic feeders to self-cleaning litter boxes, we do the research so you don't have to.</p>

    <h2>How We Test</h2>
    <p>Every product we review goes through a multi-point evaluation:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Hands-on testing</strong> — We use each product with real pets for at least two weeks</li>
      <li><strong>App evaluation</strong> — We test connectivity, scheduling, and reliability across iOS and Android</li>
      <li><strong>User feedback analysis</strong> — We aggregate thousands of verified buyer reviews to spot patterns</li>
      <li><strong>Value assessment</strong> — We compare features vs. price across the entire category</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Trust Us?</h2>
    <p>We are independently owned and operated. Our recommendations are based on testing and research, not brand relationships. While we earn commissions through affiliate links (at no cost to you), our reviews and rankings are never influenced by advertiser relationships.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>Pet lovers, tech enthusiasts, and obsessive researchers. We've collectively tested over 50 smart pet devices and counting.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions, suggestions, or a product you'd like us to review? Reach us at hello@smartpetguide.com.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
